name: Venomskull Serpent
text:
Deathtouch
Flood {1}{b}{b}{b} ({1}{b}{b}{b}, Exile this card from your hand: Target land loses all land types and abilities and has "{T}: Add {c}." Flood only as a sorcery.) 
Whenever you flood Venomskull Serpent or it enters the battlefield, target player discards two cards.
